{"tid":1353704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[727] 光復元朗牌頭一定要和理非+自衛反擊","createTime":"2019-07-23T04:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T04:16:18.000Z","uid":61886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d4a8dde4c6813c8b1931928407c207df956af738","tid":1353704,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:10:18.000Z","msg":"每次遊行都一定要夠多人<br />\n由和理非cover勇武<br />\n先係最大成效<br />\n<br />\n勇武到時做咩自己決定<br />\n(個人不建議入村 村入面隨時有埋伏)<br />\n不值得同班牛屎佬搏命<br />\n但點都要搞鳩佢地<br />\n<br />\n不過最少要確保和理非安全<br />\n<br />\n唔好太渲染一定放火打架劈友燒村<br />\n搞到和理非唔敢出<br />\n得一千幾百人出<br />\n就好危險<br />\n<br />\n所以牌頭一定要打和理非+自衛反擊<br />\n<br />\n到時做咩 現場決定<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n<br />\n同埋真係唔好戀戰<br />\n一少人就會比人警黑合作<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"9e14a7c93d57a74701fea0abc7b9e8c2569224a9","tid":1353704,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06487ab1561e0a69ebe012f74a9c42b4fc3a4440","tid":1353704,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84449d885c590e574f299545d01504e9a45c5671","tid":1353704,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3588f4881b862763c00539c6f96fd8dcab28771d","tid":1353704,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:16:18.000Z","msg":"用反恐牌頭好過啦"}]}